{
  "ver": "3.0",
  "name": "无知",
  "startPosition": { "x": 0, "y": 2, "z": 0 },
  "platforms": [
    { "id": "1", "x": 0, "y": 0.5, "z": 0, "width": 10, "depth": 10, "height": 1, "type": 1, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "2", "x": 12, "y": 1.5, "z": 0, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "3", "x": 24, "y": 3, "z": 0, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "4", "x": 36, "y": 4.5, "z": 0, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "5", "x": 48, "y": 6, "z": 0, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 2, "tooltip": "这世上的道路有许多条，而每个人都有属于自己的那条。", "tooltip_en": "There are many roads in this world, and everyone has their own." },
    { "id": "6", "x": 48, "y": 6, "z": -12, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "7", "x": 36, "y": 5, "z": -12, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "8", "x": 24, "y": 4, "z": -12, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "9", "x": 12, "y": 3, "z": -12, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "在一个充满绝望的地方，没有人会去质疑一份希望的重量。", "tooltip_en": "In a place full of despair, no one questions the weight of a hope." },
    { "id": "10", "x": 0, "y": 2, "z": -12, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "11", "x": -12, "y": 3, "z": -12, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "12", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -12, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "我的人生是一条只能向前推进的窄路，头顶是开刃的刀，身后是吃人的鬼。", "tooltip_en": "My life is a narrow path that can only move forward, with a sharpened blade above my head and man-eating ghosts behind me." },
    { "id": "13", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -24, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "14", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -24, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "15", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -24, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 2, "tooltip": "希望是最残忍的东西，因为它让人在绝望中继续受苦。", "tooltip_en": "Hope is the cruelest thing, because it makes people continue to suffer in despair." },
    { "id": "16", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -24, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "17", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -24, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "18", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -24, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "做过的决定永不回想，走过的路永不回看。", "tooltip_en": "Never look back on decisions made, never look back on roads traveled." },
    { "id": "19", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -36, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "20", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -36, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "21", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -36, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 2, "tooltip": "这世上没有绝望的处境，只有对处境绝望的人。", "tooltip_en": "There is no desperate situation in this world, only people who are desperate about the situation." },
    { "id": "22", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -36, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "23", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -36, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "24", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -36, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "我们年少时死在了过去，我们成年后依然死在了过去。", "tooltip_en": "We died in the past when we were young, and we still die in the past when we grow up." },
    { "id": "25", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -48, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "26", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -48, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "27", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -48, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 2, "tooltip": "活着不是胜利，活得像个人才是。", "tooltip_en": "Living is not victory, living like a human being is." },
    { "id": "28", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -48, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "29", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -48, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "30", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -48, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "这里没有退路。", "tooltip_en": "There is no way back here." },
    { "id": "31", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -60, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "32", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -60, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "33", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -60, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 2, "tooltip": "我肮脏了一辈子，死的时候我想干净一点。", "tooltip_en": "I have been dirty all my life, I want to be clean when I die." },
    { "id": "34", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -60, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "35", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -60, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "36", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -60, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "这场战只能我一个人打。", "tooltip_en": "This battle can only be fought by me alone." },
    { "id": "37", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -72, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "38", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -72, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "39", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -72, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 2, "tooltip": "路只有一条，向前或停下。", "tooltip_en": "There is only one road, forward or stop." },
    { "id": "40", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -72, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "41", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -72, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "42", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -72, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "没有人会去质疑一份希望的重量。", "tooltip_en": "No one questions the weight of a hope." },
    { "id": "43", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -84, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "44", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -84, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "45", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -84, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 2, "tooltip": "碎过的镜子，补好也不是新的。", "tooltip_en": "A broken mirror, even mended, is not new." },
    { "id": "46", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -84, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "47", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -84, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "48", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -84, "width": 8, "depth": 8, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "希望让人在绝望中继续受苦。", "tooltip_en": "Hope makes people continue to suffer in despair." },
    { "id": "49", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -96, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "50", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -96, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "51", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -96, "width": 10, "depth": 10, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "弱者遵守规则，强者制定规则。", "tooltip_en": "The weak follow the rules, the strong make the rules." },
    { "id": "52", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -96, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "53", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -96, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "54", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -96, "width": 10, "depth": 10, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "信任是这里最贵的奢侈品，但你不得不买。", "tooltip_en": "Trust is the most expensive luxury here, but you have to buy it." },
    { "id": "55", "x": 36, "y": 9.5, "z": -108, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "56", "x": 24, "y": 8.5, "z": -108, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "57", "x": 12, "y": 7.5, "z": -108, "width": 10, "depth": 10, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "只要不回头看，你就永远错不了，你做出的每个选择都是对的。", "tooltip_en": "As long as you don't look back, you can never be wrong, every choice you make is right." },
    { "id": "58", "x": 0, "y": 6.5, "z": -108, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "59", "x": -12, "y": 5.5, "z": -108, "width": 5, "depth": 5, "height": 1, "type": 0, "tooltip": "", "tooltip_en": "" },
    { "id": "60", "x": -24, "y": 4.5, "z": -108, "width": 12, "depth": 12, "height": 1, "type": 3, "tooltip": "畏手畏脚会让你暂时安全，但会永远危险。", "tooltip_en": "Hesitation will keep you safe for a while, but forever dangerous." }
  ],
